vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting the renewal of Specific Use Permit No. 2317 for a multifamily use on property zoned Planned Development District No. 407, on the south line of Kiest Boulevard and the east side of Boulder Drive
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval for a five-year period, subject to conditions
